Case 1. Successful login

Steps:
1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com
2. Enter "Student" in the "Email" input , "909090" in input "Password"
3. Press the button "Вход"

Expected results: Successful login. Opening the main page.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Case 2. Successful Adding New Employee

Pre-Conditions: Successful login from Case 1
Steps:
1. Click the menu item "Словари"
2. Click on the sub-item "Сотрудники"
3. Press the "+ (Add)" button
4. Fill in the fields Worker surname, Worker name, Worker middle name, Worker phone with values Test 1/2/3/4
5. Click the button "Создать"
6. Check whether the created employee is in the "Employees" list

Expected results: Successful employee creation and adding it to the grid.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Case 3. Adding New spare

Pre-Conditions: Successful login from Case 1
Steps:
1. Click the menu item "Словари"
2. Click the menu item "Запчаcти"
3. Press the "+ (Add)" button
4. Enter TestName in the field "Spare name"
5. Click in the dropdown "Тип Детали" and select "Механика"
6. Click the button "Создать"
7. Check whether the created employee is in the “Spare” list

Expected results: Successful spare creation and adding it to the grid.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Case 4. Opening user profile

Pre-Conditions: Successful login from Case 1
Steps:
1. Click the button with user icon in the upper right corner
2. In the pop-up press the button "Профиль"

Expected results: Opening user profile

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Case 5. Add New Deal

Pre-Conditions: Successful login from Case 1
Steps:
1. Click the menu item "Сделки"
2. Click the menu item "Словари"
3. In the "Deal date", "Тип сделки" "Покупатель" "Поставищик" field, select random data from the dropouts
4. Click the button "Создать"
5. Check whether the created employee is in the "Deal" list

Expected results: Successful Deal creation and adding it to the grid.

